engthen the evidence that {\\it if} the KKLT\nconstruction is meta-stable, it is indeed a spontaneously SUSY-broken (and\ntherefore bona fide) vacuum of string theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Sep 2018 16:04:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-17"}
