 points according\nto the sign of $b(z)\\cdot\\vec{n}(z)$, where $z\\in\\partial D$ and $\\vec{n}(z)$\nis the unit outward normal vector. Finally, we provide an example and simulate\nit by Monte-Carlo method to show our results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 15 Sep 2018 13:20:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-18"}
